rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: EXTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if the bdq:SourceAuthority is not available; INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if the dwc:countryCode was EMPTY; COMPLIANT if dwc:countryCode is a valid ISO (ISO 3166-1-alpha-2 country codes) value; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_COUNTRYCODE_STANDARD

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is the value of dwc:countryCode a valid ISO country code value?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is the value of dwc:countryCode a valid ISO country code value? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: EXTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if the bdq:sourceAuthority is not available; INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:country was EMPTY; COMPLIANT if value of dwc:country is a place type equivalent to "nation" by the bdq:sourceAuthority; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_COUNTRY_STANDARD

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Does the value of dwc:country occur in bdq:sourceAuthority?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Does the value of dwc:country occur in bdq:sourceAuthority? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: EXTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if the bdq:sourceAuthority is not available; INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:phylum is EMPTY; COMPLIANT if the value of dwc:phylum was found as a value at the rank of Phylum by the bdq:sourceAuthority; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_PHYLUM_FOUND

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Does the value of dwc:gphylum occur at rank of Phylum in bdq:sourceAuthority?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Does the value of dwc:gphylum occur at rank of Phylum in bdq:sourceAuthority? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:occurrenceID is EMPTY; COMPLIANT if the value of dwc:occurrenceID follows a format commonly associated with globally unique identifiers (GUIDs); otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_OCCURRENCEID_STANDARD

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Does the value of dwc:occurrenceID occur in bdqSourceAuthority?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Does the value of dwc:occurrenceID occur in bdqSourceAuthority? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:minimumDepthInMeters or dwc:maximumDepthInMeters is EMPTY, or if either are interpretable as not zero or a positive number; COMPLIANT if the value of dwc:minimumDepthInMeters is less than or equal to the value of dwc:maximumDepthInMeters; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_MINDEPTH_LESSTHAN_MAXDEPTH

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is the value of dwc:minimumDepthInMeters a number that is less than or equal to the value of dwc:maximumDepthInMeters?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is the value of dwc:minimumDepthInMeters a number that is less than or equal to the value of dwc:maximumDepthInMeters? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:dateIdentified is EMPTY; AMENDED the value of dwc:dateIdentified if it can be unambiguously interpreted as a valid ISO 8601-1:2019 date; otherwise NOT_AMENDED
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: AMENDMENT_DATEIDENTIFIED_STANDARDIZED

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Proposed amendment to the value of dwc:dateIdentified to a valid ISO date.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Proposed amendment to the value of dwc:dateIdentified to a valid ISO date.Amedment for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: EXTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if the bdq:sourceAuthority is not available; INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:family is EMPTY; COMPLIANT if the value of dwc:family was found as a value at the rank of Family by the bdq:sourceAuthority; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_FAMILY_FOUND

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Does the value of dwc:family occur at rank of Family in bdq:sourceAuthority?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Does the value of dwc:family occur at rank of Family in bdq:sourceAuthority? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:decimalLongitude is EMPTY or the value is not a number; COMPLIANT if the value of dwc:decimalLongitude is between -180 and 180 degrees, inclusive; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_DECIMALLONGITUDE_INRANGE

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is the value of dwc:decimalLongitude a number between -180 and 180?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is the value of dwc:decimalLongitude a number between -180 and 180? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if Verbatim coordinates (either dwc:verbatimLatitude and dwc:verbatimLongitude or dwc:verbatimCoordinates) were not interpretable into coordinates as decimal degrees or either dwc:decimalLatitude or dwc:decimalLongitude was not EMPTY; AMENDED the values of dwc:decimalLatitude and dwc:decimalLongitude from unambiguous values in dwc:verbatimCoordinates or dwc:verbatimLatitude and dwc:verbatimLongitude, plus dwc:verbatimCoordinateSystem and dwc:verbatimSRS; otherwise NOT_AMENDED
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: AMENDMENT_COORDINATES_FROM_VERBATIM

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Proposed amendment tothe values of dwc:decimalLatitude and dwc:decimalLongitude from information in the verbatim coordinates terms.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Proposed amendment tothe values of dwc:decimalLatitude and dwc:decimalLongitude from information in the verbatim coordinates terms.Amedment for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: COMPLIANT if dwc:eventDate is not EMPTY; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_EVENTDATE_NOTEMPTY

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is there a value in dwc:eventDate?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is there a value in dwc:eventDate? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:eventDate is EMPTY or if the value of dwc:eventDate is not a valid ISO 8601-1:2019 date; COMPLIANT if the range of dwc:eventDate is entirely within the range bdq:earliestValidDate to bdq:latestValidDate, otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_EVENTDATE_INRANGE

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is the value of dwc:eventDate entirely with the Parameter Range?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is the value of dwc:eventDate entirely with the Parameter Range? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: EXTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if the bdq:sourceAuthority is not available; INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dcterms:license is EMPTY; COMPLIANT if the value of the term dcterms:license is in the bdq:sourceAuthority; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_LICENSE_STANDARD

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Does the value of dcterms:license occur in bdq:sourceAuthority?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Does the value of dcterms:license occur in bdq:sourceAuthority? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:minimumElevationInMeters is EMPTY or the value is not a number; COMPLIANT if the value of dwc:minimumElevationInMeters is within the range of bdq:minimumValidElevationInMeters to bdq:maximumValidElevationInMeters inclusive; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_MINELEVATION_INRANGE

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is the value of dwc:minimumElevationInMeters within the Parameter range?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is the value of dwc:minimumElevationInMeters within the Parameter range? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: COMPLIANT if at least one term needed to determine the location of the entity exists and is not EMPTY; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_LOCATION_NOTEMPTY

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is there a value in any of the Darwin Core spatial terms that could identify a location?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is there a value in any of the Darwin Core spatial terms that could identify a location? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: EXTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if the DCMI (Dublin Core Metadata Initiative) service is not available; INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if the value of dc:type is EMPTY; AMENDED the value of dc:type if it matched a value in the DCMI type vocabulary; otherwise NOT_AMENDED
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: AMENDMENT_DCTYPE_STANDARDIZED

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Standardize the value of dc:type using the DCMI type vocabulary.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Standardize the value of dc:type using the DCMI type vocabulary.Amedment for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: COMPLIANT if dwc:country is not EMPTY; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_COUNTRY_NOTEMPTY

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is there a value in dwc:country?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is there a value in dwc:country? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:decimalLatitude or dwc:decimalLongitude or dwc:geodeticDatum are EMPTY or not interpretable; AMENDED the values of dwc:decimalLatitude, dwc:decimalLongitude and dwc:geodeticDatum by a conversion between spatial reference systems; otherwise NOT_AMENDED
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: AMENDMENT_COORDINATES_CONVERTED

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Proposed amendment to the values of dwc:decimalLatitude or dwc:decimalLongitude or dwc:geodeticDatum based on a conversion between spatial reference systems.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Proposed amendment to the values of dwc:decimalLatitude or dwc:decimalLongitude or dwc:geodeticDatum based on a conversion between spatial reference systems.Amedment for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: EXTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if the bdq:sourceAuthority is not available; INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:scientificName is EMPTY; COMPLIANT if there is a match of the contents of dwc:scientificName with the bdq:sourceAuthority; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_SCIENTIFICNAME_FOUND

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is there a match of the contents of dwc:scientificName with bdq:sourceAuthority?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is there a match of the contents of dwc:scientificName with bdq:sourceAuthority? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: COMPLIANT if dwc:occurrenceID is not EMPTY; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_OCCURRENCEID_NOTEMPTY

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is there a value in dwc:occurrenceID?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is there a value in dwc:occurrenceID? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: EXTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if the ISO 3166 service is not available; INTERNAL_PREREQUISTITES_NOT_MET if the value of dwc:countryCode is EMPTY; AMENDED the value of dwc:countryCode if a valid ISO 3166-1-alpha-2 country code could be unambiguously interpreted; otherwise NOT_AMENDED
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: AMENDMENT_COUNTRYCODE_STANDARDIZED

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Standardize the value of dwc:countryCode to a valid ISO country code.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Standardize the value of dwc:countryCode to a valid ISO country code.Amedment for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: COMPLIANT if dwc:year is not EMPTY; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_YEAR_NOTEMPTY

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is there a value in dwc:year?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is there a value in dwc:year? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: EXTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if the bdq:sourceAuthority is not available; INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if one or more of dwc:decimalLatitude, dwc:decimalLongitude, or dwc:countryCode are EMPTY or contain values that cannot be interpreted; COMPLIANT if the geographic coordinates fall on or within the boundary defined by the union of the boundary of the country from dwc:countryCode plus it's Exclusive Economic Zone, if any, plus an exterior buffer given by bdq:spatialBufferInMeters; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_COORDINATES_COUNTRYCODE_CONSISTENT

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Do the geographic coordinates fall on or within the boundaries of the country (from dwc:countryCode ) plus its Exclusive Economic Zone?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Do the geographic coordinates fall on or within the boundaries of the country (from dwc:countryCode ) plus its Exclusive Economic Zone? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: EXTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if either bdq:sourceAuthority[taxonomyismarine] or bdq:sourceAuthority[geospatialland] are not available; INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:dcientificName was EMPTY or the marine/non-marine status of the taxon is not interpretable from bdq:sourceAuthority[taxonomyismarine] or the values of dwc:decimalLatitude or dwc:decimalLongitude are EMPTY; COMPLIANT if the taxon marine/non-marine status from bdq:sourceAuthority[taxonomyismarine] matches the marine/non-marine status of dwc:decimalLatitude and dwc:decimalLongitude on the boundaries given by bdq:sourceAuthority[geospatialland] plus an exterior buffer given by bdq:spatialBufferInMeters; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_COORDINATES_TERRESTRIALMARINE

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Does the marine/nonmarine status of a taxon from bdq:sourceAuthority[taxonomyismarine] match the location given by the coordinates?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Does the marine/nonmarine status of a taxon from bdq:sourceAuthority[taxonomyismarine] match the location given by the coordinates? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:eventDate is EMPTY or does not contain a valid ISO 8601-1:2019 date; AMENDED one or more EMPTY terms dwc:year, dwc:month, dwc:day, dwc:startDayOfYear, dwc:endDayOfYear if they can be unambiguously interpreted from values in dwc:eventDate, and dwc:eventDate is wholly within one year; otherwise NOT_AMENDED
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: AMENDMENT_EVENT_FROM_EVENTDATE

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Proposed amendment to values in any of dwc:year, dwc:month, dwc:day, dwc:startDayOfYear or dwc:endDayOfYear from a value in dwc:eventDate.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Proposed amendment to values in any of dwc:year, dwc:month, dwc:day, dwc:startDayOfYear or dwc:endDayOfYear from a value in dwc:eventDate.Amedment for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if any of dwc:decimalLatitude or dwc:decimalLongitude or dwc:countryCode are EMPTY; AMENDED dwc:decimalLatitude and dwc:decimalLongitude if the coordinates were transposed or one or more of the signs of the coordinates were reversed to place the record in the region defined by the supplied dwc:countryCode; otherwise NOT_AMENDED
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: AMENDMENT_COORDINATES_TRANSPOSED

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Proposed amendment of the signs of dwc:decimalLatitude and/or dwc:decimalLongitude to place the record in the region defined by the supplied dwc:countryCode
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Proposed amendment of the signs of dwc:decimalLatitude and/or dwc:decimalLongitude to place the record in the region defined by the supplied dwc:countryCodeAmedment for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:verbatimDepth is EMPTY or the value is not unambiguously interpretable or dwc:minimumDepthInMeters and dwc:maximumDepthInMeters are not EMPTY; AMENDED the value of dwc:minimumDepthInMeters and/or dwc:maximumDepthInMeters if they were unambiguously determined from dwc:verbatimDepth; otherwise NOT_AMENDED
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: AMENDMENT_MINDEPTH-MAXDEPTH_FROM_VERBATIM

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Proposed amendments of the values of dwc:minimumDepthInMeters and/or dwc:maximumDepthInMeters if they can be unambiguously determined from values in dwc:verbatimDepth.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Proposed amendments of the values of dwc:minimumDepthInMeters and/or dwc:maximumDepthInMeters if they can be unambiguously determined from values in dwc:verbatimDepth.Amedment for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: EXTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if the bdq:sourceAuthority was not available; INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if the values of dwc:decimalLatitude, dwc:decimalLongitude, or dwc:stateProvince are EMPTY; COMPLIANT if the geographic coordinates fall on or within the bdq:spatialBufferInMeters boundary of the geometry of the given dwc:stateProvince after coordinate reference system transformations, if any, have been accounted for; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_COORDINATES_STATEPROVINCE_CONSISTENT

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Do the geographic coordinates fall on or within the bdq:spatialBufferInMeters boundary of the given dwc:stateProvince?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Do the geographic coordinates fall on or within the bdq:spatialBufferInMeters boundary of the given dwc:stateProvince? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:taxonID is not EMPTY or if all of dwc:scientificName, dwc:genericName, dwc:specificEpithet, dwc:infraspecificEpithet, dwc:scientificNameAuthorship, and dwc:cultivarEpithet are EMPTY, AMENDED the value of taxonID for an unambiguously resolved single taxon record in the bdq:sourceAuthority through (1) the value of dwc:scientificName or (2) if dwc:scientificName is EMPTY through values of the terms dwc:genericName, dwc:specificEpithet, dwc:infraspecificEpithet, dwc:scientificNameAuthorship and dwc:cultivarEpithet, or (3) if ambiguity produced by multiple matches in (1) or (2) can be disambiguated to a single Taxon using the values of dwc:subgenus, dwc:genus, dwc:subfamily, dwc:family, dwc:order, dwc:class, dwc:phylum, dwc:kingdom, dwc:higherClassification, dwc:scientificNameID, dwc:acceptedNameUsageID, dwc:originalNameUsageID, dwc:taxonConceptID, dwc:taxonomicRank, and dwc:vernacularName); otherwise NOT_AMENDED
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: AMENDMENT_TAXONID_FROM_TAXON

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Propose an amendment to the value of dwc:taxonID if it can be unambiguously resolved from bdq:sourceAuthority using the available taxon terms.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Propose an amendment to the value of dwc:taxonID if it can be unambiguously resolved from bdq:sourceAuthority using the available taxon terms.Amedment for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: COMPLIANT if dwc:basisOfRecord is not EMPTY; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_BASISOFRECORD_NOTEMPTY

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is there a value in dwc:basisOfRecord?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is there a value in dwc:basisOfRecord? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: EXTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if the bdq:sourceAuthority is not available, INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:geodeticDatum is EMPTY; COMPLIANT if the value of dwc:geodeticDatum is a valid EPSG CRS Code (with or without the "epsg" namespace prepended), or an unambiguous alphanumeric CRS or datum code; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_GEODETICDATUM_STANDARD

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Does the value of dwc:geoteticDatum occur in bdq:sourceAuthority?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Does the value of dwc:geoteticDatum occur in bdq:sourceAuthority? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: EXTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if the bdq:sourceAuthority was not available; INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:geodeticDatum is EMPTY; AMENDED the value of dwc:geodeticDatum if it matched a value in the bdq:sourceAuthority; otherwise NOT_AMENDED
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: AMENDMENT_GEODETICDATUM_STANDARDIZED

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Standardize the value of dwc:geodeticDatum using bdq:sourceAuthority.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Standardize the value of dwc:geodeticDatum using bdq:sourceAuthority.Amedment for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:eventDate is EMPTY; AMENDED if the value of dwc:eventDate was changed to unambiguously conform with an ISO 8601-1:2019 date; otherwise NOT_AMENDED
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: AMENDMENT_EVENTDATE_STANDARDIZED

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Proposed amendment of the value of dwc:eventDate to a valid ISO date.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Proposed amendment of the value of dwc:eventDate to a valid ISO date.Amedment for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: EXTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if the bdq:sourceAuthority is not available; INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if either of the terms dwc:country or dwc:countryCode are EMPTY; COMPLIANT if the value of the ISO 3166-1-alpha-2 country code determined from the value of dwc:country is equal to the value of dwc:countryCode; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_COUNTRY_COUNTRYCODE_CONSISTENT

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is the ISO country code determined from the value of dwc:country equal to the value of dwc:countryCode?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is the ISO country code determined from the value of dwc:country equal to the value of dwc:countryCode? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: EXTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if the bdq:sourceAuthority is not available; INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:basisOfRecord is EMPTY; AMENDED the value of dwc:basisOfRecord if it matched a value in bdq:sourceAuthority; otherwise NOT_AMENDED
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: AMENDMENT_BASISOFRECORD_STANDARDIZED

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Standardize the value of dwc:basisOfRecord using bdq:sourceAuthority.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Standardize the value of dwc:basisOfRecord using bdq:sourceAuthority.Amedment for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:eventDate is EMPTY; COMPLIANT if the value of dwc:eventDate is a valid ISO 8601-1:2019 date; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_EVENTDATE_STANDARD

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is the value of dwc:eventDate a valid ISO date?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is the value of dwc:eventDate a valid ISO date? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:eventDate is EMPTY, or all of dwc:year, dwc:month, dwc:day, dwc:startDayOfYear and dwc:endDayOfYear are EMPTY; COMPLIANT if all of the following conditions are met 1) the provided value of year matches the start year of the range represented by dwc:eventDate or dwc:year is empty, and 2) the provided value in dwc:month matches the start month of the range represented by dwc:eventDate or dwc:month is empty, and 3) the provided value in dwc:day matches the start day of the range represented by dwc:eventDate or day is empty, and 4) the provided value in dwc:startDayOfYear matches the start day of the year of the range represented by dwc:eventDate or dwc:startDayOfYear is empty, and 5) the provided value in dwc:endDayOfYear matches the end day of the year the range represented by dwc:eventDate or dwc:endDayOfYear is empty; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_EVENT_CONSISTENT

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Are the values in dwc:eventDate consistent with the values in dwc:year, dwc:month, dwc:day, dwc:startDayOfYear and dwc:endDayOfYear?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Are the values in dwc:eventDate consistent with the values in dwc:year, dwc:month, dwc:day, dwc:startDayOfYear and dwc:endDayOfYear? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:verbatimElevation is EMPTY or the value is not unambiguously interpretable or dwc:minimumElevationInMeters and/or dwc:maximumElevationInMeters are not EMPTY; AMENDED the values of dwc:minimumElevationInMeters and/or dwc:maximumElevationInMeters if they could be unambiguously interpreted from dwc:verbatimElevation; otherwise NOT_AMENDED
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: AMENDMENT_MINELEVATION-MAXELEVATION_FROM_VERBATIM

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Proposed amendment(s) to the values of dwc:minimumElevationInMeters and/or dwc:maximumElevationInMeters if they can be unambiguously interpreted from values in dwc:verbatimElevation.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Proposed amendment(s) to the values of dwc:minimumElevationInMeters and/or dwc:maximumElevationInMeters if they can be unambiguously interpreted from values in dwc:verbatimElevation.Amedment for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:dateIdentified is EMPTY; COMPLIANT if the value of dwc:dateIdentified is a valid ISO 8601-1:2019 date; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_DATEIDENTIFIED_STANDARD

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is the value of dwc:dateIdentified a valid ISO date?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is the value of dwc:dateIdentified a valid ISO date? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: EXTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if the bdq:sourceAuthority is not available; INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if all of dwc:taxonID, dwc:scientificName, dwc:genericName, dwc:specificEpithet, dwc:infraspecificEpithet, dwc:scientificNameAuthorship, dwc:cultivarEpithet are EMPTY; COMPLIANT if (1) dwc:taxonId or dwc:scientificName reference a single taxon record in the bdq:sourceAuthority, or (2) if dwc:scientificName and dwc:taxonID are EMPTY and if a combination of the values of the terms dwc:genericName, dwc:specificEpithet, dwc:infraspecificEpithet, dwc:cultivarEpithet, dwc:taxonRank, and dwc:scientificNameAuthorship can be unambiguously resolved to a unique taxon in the bdq:sourceAuthority, or (3) if ambiguity produced by multiple matches in (2) can be disambiguated to a unique Taxon using the values of dwc:subgenus, dwc:genus, dwc:subfamily, dwc:family, dwc:order, dwc:class, dwc:phylum, dwc:kingdom, dwc:higherClassification, dwc:scientificNameID, dwc:acceptedNameUsageID, dwc:originalNameUsageID, dwc:taxonConceptID and dwc:vernacularName; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_TAXON_UNAMBIGUOUS

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Can the taxon be unambiguously resolved from bdq:sourceAuthority using the available taxon terms?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Can the taxon be unambiguously resolved from bdq:sourceAuthority using the available taxon terms? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: EXTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if the bdq:sourceAuthority is not available; INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:taxonID is EMPTY, the value of dwc:taxonID is ambiguous or dwc:scientificName was not EMPTY; AMENDED the value of dwc:scientificName if the value of dwc:taxonID was matched to a value in bdq:sourceAuthority; otherwise NOT_AMENDED
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: AMENDMENT_SCIENTIFICNAME_FROM_TAXONID

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Propose an amendment to the value of dwc:scientificName using the taxonID value from bdq:sourceAuthority.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Propose an amendment to the value of dwc:scientificName using the taxonID value from bdq:sourceAuthority.Amedment for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: POTENTIAL_ISSUE if dwc:dataGeneralizations is not EMPTY; otherwise NO_ISSUE
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: ISSUE_DATAGENERALIZATIONS_NOTEMPTY

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is there a value in dwc:dataGeneralizations?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is there a value in dwc:dataGeneralizations? Issue for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: EXTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if the bdq:sourceAuthority is not available; INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if either dwc:decimalLatitude or dwc:decimalLongitude is EMPTY or uninterpretable, or if dwc:countryCode is NOT_EMPTY; AMENDED dwc:countryCode if dwc:decimalLatitude and dwc:decimalLongitude fall within a boundary from the bdq:sourceAuthority that is attributable to a single valid ISO 3166-1-alpha-2 country code; otherwise NOT_AMENDED.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: AMENDMENT_COUNTRYCODE_FROM_COORDINATES

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Proposed amendment to the value of dwc:countryCode if dwc:decimalLatitude and dwc:decimalLongitude fall within a boundary from the bdq:sourceAuthority that is attributable to a single valid country code.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Proposed amendment to the value of dwc:countryCode if dwc:decimalLatitude and dwc:decimalLongitude fall within a boundary from the bdq:sourceAuthority that is attributable to a single valid country code.Amedment for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:occurrenceStatus is not EMPTY; AMENDED the value of dwc:occurrenceStatus using the Parameter value; otherwise NOT_AMENDED
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: AMENDMENT_OCCURRENCESTATUS_ASSUMEDDEFAULT

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Use the Default value if dwc:occurrenceStatus is EMPTY.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Use the Default value if dwc:occurrenceStatus is EMPTY.Amedment for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if any of these three conditions are met (1) dwc:dateIdentified is EMPTY, (2) dwc:dateIdentified is not a valid ISO 8601-1:2019 date, (3) dwc:eventDate is not EMPTY and is not a valid ISO 8601-1:2019 date; COMPLIANT if the value of dwc:dateIdentified is within the parameter ranges and either (1) dwc:eventDate is EMPTY or (2) if dwc:eventDate is a valid ISO 8601-1:2019 date and dwc:dateIdentified overlaps or is later than the dwc:eventDate; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_DATEIDENTIFIED_INRANGE

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is the value of dwc:dateIdentified within Parameter ranges and either overlap or is later than dwc:eventDate?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is the value of dwc:dateIdentified within Parameter ranges and either overlap or is later than dwc:eventDate? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: EXTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if the bdq:sourceAuthority is not available; INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:class is EMPTY; COMPLIANT if the value of dwc:class was found as a value at the rank of Class by the bdq:sourceAuthority; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_CLASS_FOUND

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Does the value of dwc:class occur at rank of Class in bdq:sourceAuthority?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Does the value of dwc:class occur at rank of Class in bdq:sourceAuthority? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: COMPLIANT if dwc:geodeticDatum is not EMPTY; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_GEODETICDATUM_NOTEMPTY

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is there a value in dwc:geodeticDatum?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is there a value in dwc:geodeticDatum? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:decimalLatitude is EMPTY or the value is not interpretable as a number; COMPLIANT if the value of dwc:decimalLatitude is between -90 and 90, inclusive; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_DECIMALLATITUDE_INRANGE

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is the value of dwc:decimalLatitude a number between -90 and 90 inclusive?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is the value of dwc:decimalLatitude a number between -90 and 90 inclusive? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: EXTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if the bdq:sourceAuthority is not available; INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:kingdom is EMPTY; COMPLIANT if the value of dwc:kingdom was found as a value at the rank of kingdom by the bdq:sourceAuthority; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_KINGDOM_FOUND

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Does the value of dwc:kingdom occur at rank of Kingdom in bdq:sourceAuthority?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Does the value of dwc:kingdom occur at rank of Kingdom in bdq:sourceAuthority? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: COMPLIANT if dwc:scientificName is not EMPTY; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_SCIENTIFICNAME_NOTEMPTY

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is there a value in dwc:scientificName?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is there a value in dwc:scientificName? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: EXTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if the bdq:sourceAuthority is not available; INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:order is EMPTY; COMPLIANT if the value of dwc:order was found as a value at the rank of Order by the bdq:sourceAuthority; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_ORDER_FOUND

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Does the value of dwc:order occur at rank of Order in bdq:sourceAuthority?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Does the value of dwc:order occur at rank of Order in bdq:sourceAuthority? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:year is not present, or is EMPTY or cannot be interpreted as an integer; COMPLIANT if the value of dwc:year is within the Parameter range; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_YEAR_INRANGE

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is the value of dwc:year within the Parameter range?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is the value of dwc:year within the Parameter range? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:eventDate is not EMPTY or the value of dwc:verbatimEventDate is EMPTY or not unambiguously interpretable as an ISO 8601-1:2019 date; AMENDED the value of dwc:eventDate if an unambiguous ISO 8601-1:2019 date was interpreted from dwc:verbatimEventDate; otherwise NOT_AMENDED
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: AMENDMENT_EVENTDATE_FROM_VERBATIM

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Propose amendment to the value of dwc:eventDate from values in dwc:verbatimEventDate.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Propose amendment to the value of dwc:eventDate from values in dwc:verbatimEventDate.Amedment for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:decimalLatitude and/or dwc:decimalLongitude are EMPTY or both of the values are not interpretable as numbers; COMPLIANT if either the value of dwc:decimalLatitude is not = 0 or the value of dwc:decimalLongitude is not = 0; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_COORDINATES_NOTZERO

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Are the values of either dwc:decimalLatitude or dwc:decimalLongitude numbers that are not = 0?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Are the values of either dwc:decimalLatitude or dwc:decimalLongitude numbers that are not = 0? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: COMPLIANT if any of dwc:eventDate, dwc:year, dwc:month, dwc:day, dwc:startDayOfYear, dwc:endDayOfYear, dwc:verbatimEventDate are NOT EMPTY; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_EVENT_TEMPORAL_NOTEMPTY

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is there a value in any of the terms dwc:eventDate, dwc:year, dwc:month, dwc:day, dwc:startDayOfYear, dwc:endDayOfYear, dwc:verbatimEventDate?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is there a value in any of the terms dwc:eventDate, dwc:year, dwc:month, dwc:day, dwc:startDayOfYear, dwc:endDayOfYear, dwc:verbatimEventDate? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: EXTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if the DCMI (Dublin Core Metadata Initiative) service is not available; INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if the value of dc:type is EMPTY; COMPLIANT if the value of dc:type is among the values in the DCMI type vocabulary; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_DCTYPE_STANDARD

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Does the value in dc:type occur in bdq:sourceAuthority?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Does the value in dc:type occur in bdq:sourceAuthority? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL _PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:eventDate is not EMPTY or dwc:year is EMPTY or is uninterpretable as a valid year; AMENDED the value of dwc:eventDate if an unambiguous ISO 8601-1:2019 date can be interpreted from the values in dwc:year, dwc:month and dwc:day; otherwise NOT_AMENDED
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: AMENDMENT_EVENTDATE_FROM_YEARMONTHDAY

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Propose amendment to the value of dwc:eventDate from values in dwc:year, dwc:month and dwc:day.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Propose amendment to the value of dwc:eventDate from values in dwc:year, dwc:month and dwc:day.Amedment for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: POTENTIAL_ISSUE if dwc:establishmentMeans is not EMPTY; otherwise NO_ISSUE
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: ISSUE_ESTABLISHMENTMEANS_NOTEMPTY

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is there a value in dwc:establishmentMeans?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is there a value in dwc:establishmentMeans? Issue for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: EXTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if the bdq:sourceAuthority is not available; INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if all of the terms dwc:continent, dwc:country, dwc:countryCode, dwc:stateProvince, dwc:county, dwc:municipality are EMPTY; COMPLIANT if the combination of values of dwc:continent, dwc:country, dwc:countryCode, dwc:stateProvince, dwc:county, dwc:municipality can be unambiguously resolved by the bdq:sourceAuthority; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_GEOGRAPHY_UNAMBIGUOUS

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Can the combination of the values of the terms dwc:continent, dwc:country, dwc:countryCode, dwc:stateProvince, dwc:county, dwc:municipality be unambiguously resolved from bdq:sourceAuthority?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Can the combination of the values of the terms dwc:continent, dwc:country, dwc:countryCode, dwc:stateProvince, dwc:county, dwc:municipality be unambiguously resolved from bdq:sourceAuthority? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: COMPLIANT if dwc:decimalLongitude is not EMPTY; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_DECIMALLONGITUDE_NOTEMPTY

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is there a value in dwc:decimalLongitude?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is there a value in dwc:decimalLongitude? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: COMPLIANT if dwc:countryCode is not EMPTY; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_COUNTRYCODE_NOTEMPTY

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is there a value in dwc:countryCode?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is there a value in dwc:countryCode? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: COMPLIANT if dcterms:license is not EMPTY; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_LICENSE_NOTEMPTY

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is there a value in dcterms:license?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is there a value in dcterms:license? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:scientificName is EMPTY, or all of dwc:genericName, dwc:specificEpithet and dwc:infraspecificEpithet are EMPTY; COMPLIANT if the polynomial, as represented in dwc:scientificName, is consistent with the atomic parts dwc:genericName, dwc:specificEpithet, dwc:infraspecificEpithet; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_POLYNOMIAL_CONSISTENT

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is the polynomial represented in dwc:scientificName consistent with the equivalent values in dwc:genericName, dwc:specificEpithet, dwc:infraspecificEpithet?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is the polynomial represented in dwc:scientificName consistent with the equivalent values in dwc:genericName, dwc:specificEpithet, dwc:infraspecificEpithet? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: AMENDED the value of dwc:geodeticDatum to the value of bdq:defaultGeodeticDatum if dwc:geodeticDatum is EMPTY; otherwise NOT_AMENDED
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: AMENDMENT_GEODETICDATUM_ASSUMEDDEFAULT

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: If dwc:geodeticDatum is empty, amended to the value of bdq:defaultGeodeticDatum.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: If dwc:geodeticDatum is empty, amended to the value of bdq:defaultGeodeticDatum.Amedment for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: COMPLIANT if dc:type is not EMPTY; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_DCTYPE_NOTEMPTY

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is there a value in dc:type?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is there a value in dc:type? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: EXTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if the bdq:sourceAuthority is not available; INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:basisOfRecord is EMPTY; COMPLIANT if the value of dwc:basisOfRecord is valid using the bdq:sourceAuthority; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_BASISOFRECORD_STANDARD

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Does the value of dwc:basisOfRecord occur in bdq:sourceAuthority?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Does the value of dwc:basisOfRecord occur in bdq:sourceAuthority? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: COMPLIANT if at least one term needed to determine the taxon of the entity exists and is not EMPTY; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_TAXON_NOTEMPTY

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is there a value in any of the terms needed to determine that the taxon exists?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is there a value in any of the terms needed to determine that the taxon exists? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:minimumDepthInMeters is EMPTY, or the value is not interpretable as zero or a positive number; COMPLIANT if the value of dwc:minimumDepthInMeters is within the range of bdq:minimumValidDepthInMeters to bdq:maximumValidDepthInMeters inclusive; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_MINDEPTH_INRANGE

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is the value of dwc:minimumDepthInMeters within the Parameter range?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is the value of dwc:minimumDepthInMeters within the Parameter range? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:maximumlevationInMeters or dwc:minimumElevationInMeters is EMPTY, or if either is not a number; COMPLIANT if the value of dwc:minimumElevationInMeters is a number less than or equal to the value of the number dwc:maximumElevationInMeters, otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_MINELEVATION_LESSTHAN_MAXELEVATION

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is the value of dwc:minimumElevationInMeters a number less than or equal to the value of dwc:maximumElevationInMeters?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is the value of dwc:minimumElevationInMeters a number less than or equal to the value of dwc:maximumElevationInMeters? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:coordinateUncertaintyInMeters is EMPTY; COMPLIANT if the value of dwc:coordinateUncertaintyInMeters can be interpreted as a number between 1 and 20037509 inclusive; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_COORDINATEUNCERTAINTY_INRANGE

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is the value of dwc:coordinateUncertaintyInMeters a number between 1 and 20,037,509?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is the value of dwc:coordinateUncertaintyInMeters a number between 1 and 20,037,509? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:maximumElevationInMeters is EMPTY or the value cannot be interpreted as a number; COMPLIANT if the value of dwc:maximumElevationInMeters is within the range of bdq:minimumValidElevationInMeters to bdq:maximumValidElevationInMeters inclusive; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_MAXELEVATION_INRANGE

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is the value of dwc:maximumElevationInMeters within the Parameter range?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is the value of dwc:maximumElevationInMeters within the Parameter range? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: EXTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if the bdq:sourceAuthority is not available; INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:ocurrenceStatus is EMPTY; AMENDED the value of dwc:occurrenceStatus if it matched a value in bdq:sourceAuthority; otherwise NOT_AMENDED
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: AMENDMENT_OCCURRENCESTATUS_STANDARDIZED

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Standardize the value of dwc:occurrenceStatus using bdq:sourceAuthority.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Standardize the value of dwc:occurrenceStatus using bdq:sourceAuthority.Amedment for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: EXTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if the bdq:sourceAuthority is not available; INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:occurrenceStatus is EMPTY; COMPLIANT if the value of dwc:occurrenceStatus is resolved by the bdq:sourceAuthority; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_OCCURRENCESTATUS_STANDARD

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Does the value of dwc:occurrenceStatus occur in bdq:sourceAuthority?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Does the value of dwc:occurrenceStatus occur in bdq:sourceAuthority? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: COMPLIANT if dwc:occurrenceStatus is not EMPTY; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_OCCURRENCESTATUS_NOTEMPTY

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is there a value in dwc:occurrenceStatus?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is there a value in dwc:occurrenceStatus? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Standardize one or more of the values of the administrative geographic terms dwc:continent, dwc:country, dwc:countryCode, dwc:stateProvince, dwc:county, dwc:municipality using bdq:sourceAuthority.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Standardize one or more of the values of the administrative geographic terms dwc:continent, dwc:country, dwc:countryCode, dwc:stateProvince, dwc:county, dwc:municipality using bdq:sourceAuthority.Amedment for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: COMPLIANT if dwc:decimalLatitude is not EMPTY; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_DECIMALLATITUDE_NOTEMPTY

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is there a value in dwc:decimalLatitude?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is there a value in dwc:decimalLatitude? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: COMPLIANT if dwc:taxonID is not EMPTY; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_TAXONID_NOTEMPTY

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is there a value in dwc:taxonID?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is there a value in dwc:taxonID? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:taxonID is EMPTY; COMPLIANT if dwc:taxonID contains both a URI and a namespace indicator; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_TAXONID_COMPLETE

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Does the value of dwc:taxonID contain both a URI and namespace indicator?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Does the value of dwc:taxonID contain both a URI and namespace indicator? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Does the value of dwc:genus occur at the rank of Genus in bdq:sourceAuthority?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Does the value of dwc:genus occur at the rank of Genus in bdq:sourceAuthority? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Can the combination of higher classification taxonomic terms be unambiguously resolved using bdq:sourceAuthority?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Can the combination of higher classification taxonomic terms be unambiguously resolved using bdq:sourceAuthority? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if (a) dwc:day is EMPTY, or (b) dwc:day is not interpretable as an integer, or (c) dwc:day is interpretable as an integer between 29 and 31 inclusive and dwc:month is not interpretable as an integer between 1 and 12, or (d) dwc:month is interpretable as the integer 2 and dwc:day is interpretable as the integer 29 and dwc:year is not interpretable as a valid ISO 8601 year; COMPLIANT if (a) the value of dwc:day is interpretable as an integer between 1 and 28 inclusive, or (b) dwc:day is interpretable as an integer between 29 and 30 and dwc:month is interpretable as an integer in the set (4,6,9,11), or (c) dwc:day is interpretable as an integer between 29 and 31 and dwc:month is interpretable as an integer in the set (1,3,5,7,8,10,12), or (d) dwc:day is interpretable as the integer 29 and dwc:month is interpretable as the integer 2 and dwc:year is interpretable as is a valid leap year (evenly divisible by 400 or (evenly divisible by 4 but not evenly divisible by 100)); otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT."
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_DAY_INRANGE

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is the value of dwc:day interpretable as a valid integer between 1 and 28 inclusive or 29, 30 or 31 given the relative month and year?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is the value of dwc:day interpretable as a valid integer between 1 and 28 inclusive or 29, 30 or 31 given the relative month and year? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:month is EMPTY; COMPLIANT if the value of dwc:month is interpretable as an integer between 1 and 12 inclusive; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_MONTH_STANDARD

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is the value of dwc:month interpretable as an integer between 1 and 12 inclusive?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is the value of dwc:month interpretable as an integer between 1 and 12 inclusive? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:day is EMPTY; AMENDED the value of dwc:day if the value was unambiguously interpreted as an integer between 1 and 31 inclusive; otherwise NOT_AMENDED
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: AMENDMENT_DAY_STANDARDIZED

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Standardize the value of dwc:day to a integer between 1 and 31 inclusive.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Standardize the value of dwc:day to a integer between 1 and 31 inclusive.Amedment for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:month is EMPTY; AMENDED the value of dwc:month if it was able to be interpreted as a integer between 1 and 12 inclusive; otherwise NOT_AMENDED
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: AMENDMENT_MONTH_STANDARDIZED

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Standardize the value of dwc:month to an integer between 1 and 12 inclusive.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Standardize the value of dwc:month to an integer between 1 and 12 inclusive.Amedment for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:startDayOfYear is EMPTY or if the value of dwc:startDayOfYear is equal to 366 and (dwc:eventDate is EMPTY or the value of dwc:eventDate can not be interpreted to find single year or a start year in a range); COMPLIANT if the value of dwc:startDayOfYear is an integer between 1 and 365, inclusive, or if the value of dwc:startDayOfYear is 366 and the start year interpreted from dwc:eventDate is a leap year; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_STARTDAYOFYEAR_INRANGE

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is the value of dwc:startDayOfYear an integer between 1 and 365 inclusive, or 366 if a leap year?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is the value of dwc:startDayOfYear an integer between 1 and 365 inclusive, or 366 if a leap year? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:endDayOfYear is EMPTY or if the value of dwc:endDayOfYear is equal to 366 and (dwc:eventDate is EMPTY or the value of dwc:eventDate cannot be interpreted to find a single year or an end year in a range); COMPLIANT if the value of dwc:endDayOfYear is an integer between 1 and 365 inclusive, or if the value of dwc:endDayOfYear is 366 and the end year interpreted from dwc:eventDate is a leap year; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_ENDDAYOFYEAR_INRANGE

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is the value of dwc:endDayOfYear an integer between 1 and 365 inclusive, or 366 if a leap year?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is the value of dwc:endDayOfYear an integer between 1 and 365 inclusive, or 366 if a leap year? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:eventDate was not EMPTY or any of dwc:year, dwc:startDayOfYear, or dwc:endDayOfYear were EMPTY or any of the values in dwc:year, dwc:startDayOfYear, or dwc:endDayOfYear were not independently interpretable; AMENDED the value of dwc:eventDate from values in dwc:year, dwc:startDayOfYear and dwc:endDayOfYear if the value of dwc:endDayOfYear is less than the value of dwc:startDayOfYear; otherwise NOT_AMENDED
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: AMENDMENT_EVENTDATE_FROM_YEARSTARTDAYOFYEARENDDAYOFYEAR

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Proposed amendment to fill in the value of dwc:eventDate from values in dwc:year, dwc:startDayOfYear and dwc:endDayOfYear.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Proposed amendment to fill in the value of dwc:eventDate from values in dwc:year, dwc:startDayOfYear and dwc:endDayOfYear.Amedment for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: EXTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if the bdq:sourceAuthority is not available; AMENDED value of dcterms:license if it matched a value in bdq:sourceAuthority; otherwise NOT_AMENDED.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: AMENDMENT_LICENSE_STANDARDIZED

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Standardize the value of dwc:license using bdq:sourceAuthority.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Standardize the value of dwc:license using bdq:sourceAuthority.Amedment for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: EXTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if the bdq:sourceAuthority is not available; INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if all of the terms dwc:continent, dwc:country, dwc:countryCode, dwc:stateProvince, dwc:county, dwc:municipality are EMPTY; COMPLIANT if the combination of values of dwc:continent, dwc:country, dwc:countryCode, dwc:stateProvince, dwc:county, dwc:municipality can be unambiguously resolved from the bdq:sourceAuthority; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_GEOGRAPHY_STANDARD

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Can the combination of the values of the terms dwc:continent, dwc:country, dwc:countryCode, dwc:stateProvince, dwc:county, dwc:municipality be unambiguously resolved from bdq:sourceAuthority?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Can the combination of the values of the terms dwc:continent, dwc:country, dwc:countryCode, dwc:stateProvince, dwc:county, dwc:municipality be unambiguously resolved from bdq:sourceAuthority? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:eventDate is EMPTY or does not contain a valid ISO 8601-1:2019 value; otherwise RUN_HAS_RESULT with the result being the duration (sensu ISO 8601-1:2019) expressed in the dwc:eventDate, in seconds.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: MEASURE_EVENTDATE_DURATIONINSECONDS

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: What is the duration of dwc:eventDate in seconds?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: What is the duration of dwc:eventDate in seconds? Measure of Resolution for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:day is EMPTY; COMPLIANT if the value of the field dwc:day is an integer between 1 and 31 inclusive; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_DAY_STANDARD

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is the value of dwc:day an integer between 1 and 31 inclusive?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is the value of dwc:day an integer between 1 and 31 inclusive? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: COMPLIANT if dwc:taxonRank is not EMPTY; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_TAXONRANK_NOTEMPTY

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is there a value in dwc:taxonRank?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is there a value in dwc:taxonRank? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: EXTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if the bdq:sourceAuthority is not available; INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:taxonRank is EMPTY; COMPLIANT if the value of dwc:taxonRank is in the bdq:sourceAuthority; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_TAXONRANK_STANDARD

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Does the value of dwc:taxonRank occur in bdq:sourceAuthority?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Does the value of dwc:taxonRank occur in bdq:sourceAuthority? Validation for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: EXTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if the bdq:sourceAuthority is not available; AMENDED the value of dwc:taxonRank if it matched a value in bdq:sourceAuthority; otherwise NOT_AMENDED
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: AMENDMENT_TAXONRANK_STANDARDIZED

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Standardize the value of dwc:taxonRank using bdq:sourceAuthority.
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Standardize the value of dwc:taxonRank using bdq:sourceAuthority.Amedment for SingleRecord

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: INTERNAL_PREREQUISITES_NOT_MET if dwc:maximumDepthInMeters is EMPTY or is not interpretable as a number; COMPLIANT if the value of dwc:maximumDepthInMeters is within the range of bdq:minimumValidDepthInMeters to bdq:maximumValidDepthInMeters inclusive; otherwise NOT_COMPLIANT
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: VALIDATION_MAXDEPTH_INRANGE

rdf:Description.rdfs:comment: Is the value of dwc:maximumDepthInMeters within the Parameter range?
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: Is the value of dwc:maximumDepthInMeters within the Parameter range? Validation for SingleRecord
